### Summary

Issue #286 asks for preference learning visibility — toasts, confidence indicators in the briefing, feedback buttons, and chat mentions. Three of four requirements are **already done**. The only remaining work is surfacing learned preferences in the `BriefingResponse` and rendering them as interactive cards in `BriefingPanel.tsx`.

